C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGielen%20sold%20her%20Tesla%20in%20part%20because%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20political%20interventions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20the%20BYD%20was%20well-built%20but%20lacked%20some%20of%20Tesla's%20technological%20features.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mahican%20Gielen%2C%20a%20radiologist%20in%20Hj%C3%B8rring%2C%20Denmark%2C%20about%20swapping%20her%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-3-review-autopilot-supercharger-photos-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETesla%20Model%203%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20for%20a%20BYD%20Sealion%207.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20Denmark%2C%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Hj%C3%B8rring%2C%20but%20we're%20actually%20from%20Holland.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20both%20doctors%3A%20I'm%20a%20radiologist%2C%20he's%20a%20cardiologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20a%20Tesla%20Model%203%20three%20years%20ago.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20electric%20car%2C%20and%20I'd%20wanted%20a%20Tesla%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20even%20pushed%20me%20because%20they%20knew%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20car.%20They%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMom%2C%20it%20should%20be%20a%20Tesla.%20That's%20the%20best%20car.%20It's%20a%20green%20car.%20It%20saves%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20say%2C%20I%20loved%20that%20car.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20big%20step%20up%20from%20the%20normal%20combustion%20engines%20and%20had%20so%20many%20cool%20features.%20I%20still%20miss%20it%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20got%20a%20bit%20annoyed%20with%20my%20Tesla%20was%20when%20the%20company%20started%20cutting%20the%20prices.%20I%20bought%20mine%20right%20before%2C%20so%20that%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-special-government-employee-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20joining%20the%20Trump%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20final%20straw.%20I%20love%20cars%2C%20but%20if%20owning%20one%20gets%20overruled%20by%20the%20constant%20noise%20about%20the%20CEO%20and%20people%20asking%20whether%20it%20bothers%20me%2C%20then%20the%20fun%20goes%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20didn't%20want%20the%20headache%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20there%20is%20more%20to%20the%20company.%20But%20when%20you%20have%20a%20CEO%20who's%20so%20visible%2C%20he%20just%20becomes%20one%20with%20the%20company.%20And%20I%20really%20feel%20bad%20for%20Tesla%20because%20I%20like%20the%20brand.%20They%20were%20so%20innovative%20and%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20was%20a%20step%20too%20far.%20It%20really%20made%20me%20say%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20this%20car.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20get%20any%20better%20from%20here%2C%20so%20I'll%20just%20cut%20my%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e87ddcc-51e6-41f4-af6d-5e3717e971e8%5C%22%3EBuying%20a%20BYD%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223496%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20front-on%20image%20of%20a%20BYD%20Sealion%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6836f2726ffb6822ec619a2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMahican%20Gielen%20replaced%20her%20Tesla%20Model%203%20with%20a%20BYD%20Sealion%207.%3Cp%3EMahican%20Gielen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20my%20Model%203%20for%20150%2C000%20Danish%20Krone%20(%2422%2C000)%20in%20April%2C%20having%20paid%20350%2C000%20Krone%20for%20it%20in%202022%2C%20and%20I%20bought%20a%20BYD%20Sealion%207%20Excellence%20the%20same%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BEditor's%20Note%3A%20BI%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20the%20purchase%20price%20of%20Gielen's%20BYD%20Sealion%207%20Excellence.%20It%20starts%20from%20around%20390%2C000%20Danish%20krone%20(%2459%2C000).%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20going%20to%20buy%20an%20SUV%2C%20but%20I%20saw%20the%20Sealion%207%20in%20a%20showroom%20and%20thought%20it%20looked%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20impulsive%2C%20but%20I'm%20really%20happy%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20build%20quality%20is%20on%20a%20level%20with%20a%20Mercedes%2C%20and%20the%20car%20feels%20really%20premium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20are%20different%2C%20but%20it%20has%20so%20many%20cool%20features%2C%20like%20a%20head-up%20display%20and%20actual%20physical%20buttons%2C%20which%20I%20missed%20as%20the%20Tesla%20didn't%20have%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20thing%20about%20the%20car%20is%20how%20solid%20it%20is.%20I%20always%20tell%20people%20the%20Tesla%20felt%20like%20a%20toy%20car%20compared%20to%20this%20one%2C%20because%20it%20was%20always%20rattling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20when%20it%20was%20freezing%2C%20you%20couldn't%20close%20the%20door%20because%20it%20wouldn't%20catch%2C%20and%20when%20you%20drove%20the%20Tesla%20around%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20sometimes%20you%20would%20hear%20sloshing%20sounds%20like%20water%20was%20dripping%20in%20the%20car.%20So%20the%20build%20quality%20is%20completely%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20range%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20for%20me%2C%20and%20the%20software%20works%20pretty%20well.%20It's%20a%20bit%20slower%20and%20less%20intuitive%20than%20the%20software%20in%20the%20Tesla%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20I%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20great%20that%20Chinese%20EV%20brands%20are%20entering%20Europe.%20I%20absolutely%20believe%20that%20the%20market%20should%20be%20open%2C%20and%20they%20have%20something%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20many%20European%20brands%20seem%20kind%20of%20boring.%20They%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20every%20time%2C%20and%20these%20brands%20do%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20people%20don't%20buy%20them%2C%20it%20will%20probably%20make%20the%20European%20brands%20push%20their%20boundaries%20a%20bit%20and%20do%20more%20stuff.%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20absolutely%20good%20for%20everyone%20if%20more%20become%20available%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220875c897-8d16-458a-be50-7056f1256cb6%5C%22%3EFeature%20FOMO%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20features%20I%20still%20miss%20about%20the%20Tesla%2C%20but%20I'm%20hoping%20they%20could%20be%20added%20to%20the%20BYD%20with%20software%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20auto-locks%20and%20unlocks%20when%20you%20just%20have%20your%20phone%20in%20your%20bag%20or%20on%20you.%20In%20the%20BYD%2C%20I%20really%20had%20to%20get%20used%20to%20pushing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20car%20key%20to%20lock%20and%20unlock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20charged%20your%20car%2C%20the%20Tesla%20automatically%20opened%20its%20charger%20port%20flap%20and%20closed%20it%20again.%20I%20have%20been%20driving%20around%20with%20an%20open%20flap%20because%20I'm%20so%20used%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20also%20really%20loved%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-features%238-air-suspension-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20'Santa%20Mode%2C'%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Tesla%20app%20has%20a%20lot%20more%20features%20than%20the%20BYD%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20I'm%20really%20going%20to%20miss%20is%20that%20Tesla%20automatically%20defrosted%20the%20windows%20via%20the%20app.%20So%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20remove%20ice%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20It's%20not%20a%20problem%20now%2C%20but%20I%20know%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20annoying%20in%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20overlook%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20were%20wrong%20with%20the%20Tesla%20because%20it%20was%20so%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20it%20was%20almost%20like%20an%20iPhone.%20But%20in%20the%20end%2C%20some%20things%20are%20just%20not%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20I%20sold%20the%20car%20was%20because%20of%20the%20build%20quality.%20Mine%20was%20beginning%20to%20get%20a%20bit%20older%2C%20and%20I%20was%20in%20the%20shop%20with%20it%20more%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20Musk%20has%20taken%20is%20extremely%20frustrating.%20It%20seriously%20hurts%20because%20I%20was%20really%20rooting%20for%20the%20brand.%20I%20think%20it's%20sad%20for%20a%20company%20that%20was%20so%20promising%20and%20could%20have%20done%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20swapped%20your%20Tesla%20for%20a%20BYD%20or%20bought%20a%20Chinese%20EV%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atcarter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etcarter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-sealion-7-i-swapped-my-tesla-for-a-byd-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748432606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6836f1d6ca50259add4d288f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-sealion-7-i-swapped-my-tesla-for-a-byd-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahican%20Gielen%2C%20who%20swapped%20her%20Tesla%20for%20a%20BYD%20Sealion%207%20partly%20because%20of%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20loves%20the%20Chinese%20EV%20but%20misses%20a%20few%20Tesla%20features.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A403%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-sealion-7-i-swapped-my-tesla-for-a-byd-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Trump's%20film%20tariffs%3A%20Is%20Hollywood%20really%20in%20decline%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748432129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121464975%2Cimgsize-1486618.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiati