tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-official-says-china-supplying-russia-military-production-factories-weapons-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748426432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d196b269253ccddf98fb13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-official-says-china-supplying-russia-military-production-factories-weapons-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ukrainian%20intelligence%20chief%20said%20China%20is%20helping%20to%20supply%20Russian%20military%20production%20plants%2C%20and%20that%20they%20have%20data%20on%2020%20factories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A240%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-official-says-china-supplying-russia-military-production-factories-weapons-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEOs%20who%20aren't%20yet%20preparing%20for%20the%20quantum%20revolution%20are%20'already%20too%20late%2C'%20IBM%20exec%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22D-Wave%20quantum%20computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F603ec64d2dc90100183550a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuantum%20computing%20will%20change%20the%20tech%20landscape%20as%20much%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20has.%20Execs%20from%20IBM%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20IonQ%2C%20PsiQuantum%2C%20and%20D-Wave%20told%20BI%20that%20corporate%20leaders%20should%20be%20preparing%20now.%3Cp%3ED-Wave%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EReady%20or%20not%2C%20the%20quantum%20computing%20revolution%20is%20nearly%20here.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20that%20don't%20evolve%20with%20the%20changing%20tech%20landscape%20risk%20falling%20behind%20their%20competitors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExecs%20from%20IBM%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20IonQ%2C%20PsiQuantum%2C%20and%20D-Wave%20say%20corporate%20leaders%20should%20prepare%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou'd%20be%20hard%20pressed%20to%20find%20a%20company%20out%20there%20that's%20not%20using%20some%20form%20of%20AI%20at%20this%20point.%20In%20just%20a%20few%20years%2C%20tech%20leaders%20say%20the%20same%20will%20be%20true%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equantum%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20equivalent%20to%20the%20exact%20thing%20that%20you're%20seeing%20with%20classical%20computing%20and%20AI%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20happen%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Gambetta%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20in%20charge%20of%20IBM's%20quantum%20initiative%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20are%20optimistic%20about%20coming%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebreakthroughs%20in%20quantum%20computing%2C%20a%20field%20that%20leverages%20quantum%20physics%20and%20mechanics%20to%20solve%20complex%20problems%20faster%20than%20is%20possible%20using%20classical%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20final%20engineering%20problems%20are%20solved%20and%20the%20technology%20scales%20up%2C%20quantum%20tech%20promises%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-could-improve-medicine-climate-logistics-world-hunger-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erevolutionize%20medicine%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20and%20more%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20say%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20quantum%20computing%20changes%20the%20tech%20landscape%20as%20much%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%2C%20so%20corporate%20leaders%20had%20better%20start%20getting%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20paying%20attention%20and%20you're%20not%20dedicating%20people%20to%20quantum%20computing%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20probably%20already%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambetta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c09e415-af7f-4e2c-9005-41a16eac833d%5C%22%3E'Future-proof'%20computing%20is%20hybrid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20and%20quantum%20computing%20are%20not%20interchangeable%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20each%20has%20its%20own%20very%20different%20strengths.%20Artificial%20intelligence%20is%20especially%20good%20at%20searching%20through%20existing%20data%20to%20make%20predictions%20about%20future%20outcomes%2C%20and%20is%20helpful%20in%20areas%20like%20image%20recognition%2C%20e-commerce%20recommendation%20engines%2C%20and%20fraud%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20utility-scale%20quantum%20computer%20doesn't%20predict%20using%20data%20from%20the%20past%2C%20Stratton%20Sclavos%2C%20PsiQuantum's%20Chief%20Business%20Officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Instead%2C%20it%20calculates%20the%20exact%20answer%20from%20first%20principles%2C%20from%20scratch%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20solve%20problems%20that%20no%20conventional%20computer%20or%20AI%20will%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20solve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20currently%20using%20or%20ramping%20up%20your%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20keep%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Sclavos%20said.%20But%2C%20he%20said%2C%20corporate%20leaders%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bpreparing%20now%20for%20how%20quantum%20computing%20will%20transform%20how%20your%20business%20operates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAseem%20Datar%2C%20Microsoft's%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20innovation%2C%20strategic%20missions%2C%20and%20technologies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20given%20the%20rapid%20pace%20of%20innovation%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20critical%20that%20organizations%20start%20exploring%2C%20identifying%2C%20and%20building%20an%20application%20road%20map%20that%20sets%20them%20up%20for%20success%20in%20a%20quantum%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20released%20Discovery%2C%20an%20agentic%20AI%20platform%20for%20scientific%20research%20and%20development%20built%20on%20top%20of%20its%20Azure%20cloud%20computing%20program.%20Datar%20said%20the%20technology%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20as%20%26quot%3Bfuture-proof%26quot%3B%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20when%20quantum%20technology%20advances%2C%20it%20will%20be%20readily%20incorporated%20into%20the%20existing%20technology%2C%20and%20users%20%26quot%3Bwill%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20quantum%20underneath%20the%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Microsoft%20Discovery%20is%20geared%20toward%20the%20scientific%20community%2C%20Datar%20said%20future-looking%20tech%20solutions%20across%20industries%20will%20share%20similar%20characteristics.%20Hybrid%20computing%20integration%2C%20which%20combines%20the%20strengths%20of%20classical%20computing%20power%20with%20those%20of%20quantum%20systems%2C%20is%20particularly%20important%2C%20he%20said%2C%20so%20corporate%20leaders%20don't%20have%20to%20rip%20and%20replace%20their%20systems%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equantum%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20reaches%20its%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurray%20Thom%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-stocks-rally-supremacy-advantage-announcement-dwave-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ED-Wave%3C%2Fa%3E's%20vice%20president%20of%20quantum%20technology%20evangelism%2C%20agreed%2C%20telling%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BHybrid%20quantum-classical%20solutions%20are%20what's%20going%20to%20give%20them%20the%20resiliency%20that%20they're%20looking%20for%20in%20their%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThom%20added%20that%20organizations%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20and%20ready%20for%20the%20speed%20of%20change%20that%20the%20tech%20landscape%20will%20undergo%20as%20quantum%20technology%20scales%20up%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20that%20they%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20technology%20and%20not%20be%20at%20a%20competitive%20disadvantage%20if%20they%20miss%20what%20the%20newest%20capabilities%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20evaluating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-race-big-tech-microsoft-google-amazon-ibm-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20there's%20the%20information%20you%20have%20about%20what's%20possible%20today%2C%20and%20then%20there's%20what%20I%20call%20a%20cone%20of%20uncertainty%20that%20projects%20into%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Thom%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20looking%20to%20gain%20information%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20narrow%20that%20cone%20of%20uncertainty%20so%20that%20you%20can%20make%20better%20business%20decisions%20about%20what%20to%20do%20today%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20that%20in%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20and%20particularly%20in%20a%20way%20that%20gives%20you%20robustness%20to%20those%20future%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c77da8c-ede6-4778-a477-5a566672c64f%5C%22%3E'The%20toothpaste%20is%20not%20going%20back%20in%20the%20tube.'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20private%20industry%20that's%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20quantum%20revolution.%20Tim%20Kelly%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Chattanooga%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he's%20investing%20heavily%20in%20his%20city's%20ability%20to%20lean%20into%20a%20quantum%20future%2C%20with%20hopes%20it%20can%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flocations-qubit-county-quantum-computing-