%20you're%20in%20venture%20capital%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20one%20of%20the%20firm's%20limited%20partners%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20strange.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20traditional%20VC%20firm%3B%20it%20now%20prefers%20to%20brand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.generalcatalyst.com%2Fworldview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eitself%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20global%20investment%20and%20transformation%20company.%26quot%3B%20Its%20leader%20since%202021%2C%20Hemant%20Taneja%2C%20holds%20the%20title%20of%20CEO%2C%20a%20common%20role%20in%20corporations%20that's%20nearly%20unheard%20of%20at%20a%20venture%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDare%20I%20say%20it%3A%20venture%20has%20gotten%20comfortable%20and%20lazy%2C%26quot%3B%20Taneja%20wrote%20in%20his%202022%20year-end%20letter%2C%20spelling%20out%20the%20firm's%20new%20direction.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20transcend%20the%20traditional%20VC%20mindset%20if%20we're%20going%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%20(Through%20a%20spokesperson%2C%20Taneja%20denied%20multiple%20interview%20requests.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20firm%20responded%20with%20written%20statements.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Taneja%2C%20GC%20has%20amassed%20stakes%20not%20only%20in%20hospitals%20but%20also%20old-line%20accounting%20firms%20and%20manufacturing%20companies.%20It's%20building%20up%20a%20wealth%20management%20business%2C%20expanding%20its%20global%20lobbying%20arm%2C%20and%20underwriting%20loans%20for%20startups%20that%20are%20more%20commonly%20the%20domain%20of%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20recently%20parted%20ways%20with%20managing%20directors%20with%20traditional%20VC%20experience%2C%20including%20Kyle%20Doherty%2C%20Adam%20Valkin%2C%20and%20Deep%20Nishar.%20Two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20other%20departures%20will%20be%20announced%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20GC%20is%20building%20up%20its%20ranks%20of%20bankers%2C%20this%20month%20adding%20longtime%20J.P.%20Morgan%20tech%20banker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmadhu-namburi-9218321%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadhu%20Namburi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20joined%20Paul%20Kwan%2C%20former%20West%20Coast%20head%20of%20tech%20banking%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20steps%20are%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20GC%20to%20someday%20be%20the%20first%20venture%20firm%20to%20go%20public%2C%20a%20person%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Although%20nothing%20has%20been%20filed%20yet%2C%20they%20said%20GC's%20IPO%20ambitions%20are%20frequently%20discussed%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20firm%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20generating%20ever-higher%20management%20fees%20to%20someday%20attract%20a%20higher%20valuation%20from%20public%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20go%20public%2C%20you%20are%20measured%20on%20your%20management%20fees%2C%20not%20on%20your%20profit%20pool%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source.%20(A%20GC%20spokesperson%20said%20no%20plans%20for%20an%20IPO%20are%20underway.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHemant%20is%20at%20a%20stage%20in%20his%20career%20where%20he's%20really%20taking%20big%20swings%20to%20leave%20a%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aniq%20Rahman%2C%20CEO%20of%20GC-backed%20Fabric%2C%20who%20added%20that%20he%20had%20no%20knowledge%20of%20any%20IPO%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22General%20Catalyst%20Hemant%20Taneja%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a2e3749fab2b00184aef60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%20CEO%20Hemant%20Taneja%20wrote%20in%202022%20that%20GC%20would%20seek%20to%20%26quot%3Btranscend%20the%20traditional%20VC%20mindset.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20GC%20is%20judged%20on%20investment%20performance%2C%20and%20the%20early%20returns%20are%20less%20than%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20last%20year%2C%20GC%20had%20a%20dismal%20internal%20rate%20of%20return%2C%20or%20IRR%2C%20of%20just%202.9%25%20across%2010%20funds%20since%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lacers.org%2Fsites%2Fmain%2Ffiles%2Ffile-attachments%2Flacers_pe_q2_2024.pdf%3F1740094321%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20filings%20from%20one%20of%20its%20investors%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20LA%20City%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System.%20The%20funds%20are%20still%20relatively%20new%20and%20could%20someday%20be%20successful.%20Still%2C%20GC%20ranked%20a%20distant%20last%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20LACERS'%20top%2010%20largest%20holdings%20and%20was%20the%20only%20one%20in%20single%20digits.%20The%20typical%20IRR%20for%205-year-old%20funds%20was%20around%2015%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridgeassociates.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2F2024-Q3-USVC-Benchmark-Book.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20data%20from%20Cambridge%20Associates.%3C%2Fa%3E(The%20GC%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20LACERS%20performance%20data%20is%20outdated%2C%20and%20that%20the%20firm's%20performance%20has%20improved%20considerably%20since%20last%20year.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20comes%20down%20to%20exits%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20healthcare%20investor%20who's%20frequently%20co-invested%20with%20General%20Catalyst.%20%26quot%3BGC%20can%20diversify%20and%20do%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%2C%20but%20LPs%20%5Blimited%20partners%5D%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20will%20look%20for%20dollars%20distributed.%20That's%20just%20the%20barometer%20of%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20sits%20among%20a%20rarefied%20handful%20of%20megafirms%20like%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20Sequoia%20Capital%20that%20are%20unlikely%20to%20achieve%20blockbuster%20venture%20returns%20but%20can%20still%20reliably%20produce%20a%20safer%20and%20smaller%20return%2C%20according%20to%20Jai%20Das%2C%20co-founder%20at%20Sapphire%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20even%20call%20them%20venture%20funds%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Das.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20almost%20like%20an%20asset%20manager%20with%20different%20products%20that%20you%20invest%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20whether%20such%20a%20sprawling%20vision%20encompassing%20more%20than%20800%20companies%20will%20pay%20off%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETaneja%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20at%20GC%20as%20an%20early%20backer%20of%20Stripe%2C%20the%20payments%20processor%20that%20is%20now%20worth%20%2491.5%20billion.%20Other%20savvy%20bets%20included%20Snap%2C%20Gitlab%2C%20and%20Gusto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20have%20known%20Taneja%20from%20his%20college%20days%20say%20he%20has%20always%20stood%20out%20as%20ambitious%20and%20smart%2C%20if%20a%20little%20unfocused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHemant%20went%20and%20got%20five%20MIT%20degrees%20before%20figuring%20out%20what%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brad%20Porter%2C%20CEO%20%26amp%3B%20Founder%20of%20GC-backed%20Collaborative%20Robotics%2C%20who%20attended%20MIT%20with%20Taneja.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20Hemant%20being%20brilliant%2C%20but%20not%20knowing%20exactly%20where%20he%20wanted%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20year%20has%20been%20a%20busy%20one%20for%20GC%20under%20Taneja.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20firm%20announced%20the%20General%20Catalyst%20Institute%2C%20a%20global%20think%20tank%20aiming%20to%20influence%20government%20tech%20policy%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20next%20month%2C%20it%20closed%20%248%20billion%20of%20new%20fundraising.%20At%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20firm%20announced%20a%20wealth%20management%20arm%2C%20GC%20Wealth%2C%20to%20provide%20investment%20advisory%20services%20with%20a%20%242.3%20billion%20pool%20of%20assets.%20(Andreesen%20Horowitz%2C%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20and%20New%20Enterprise%20Associates%20are%20among%20the%20firms%20that%20also%20offer%20wealth%20management.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20has%20also%20been%20expanding%20its%20AI-rollup%20strategy%2C%20buying%20the%20sorts%20of%20businesses%20VC%20usually%20won't%20touch%2C%20like%20accounting%20firms%20and%20call%20center%20companies%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20more%20efficient%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20now%20employs%20over%20250%20people%20to%20manage%20its%20expanding%20directives%2C%20a%20big%20jump%20from%20the%2064-person%20team%20the%20firm%20had%20before%20Taneja%20became%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20firm%20has%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20its%20involvement%20in%20the%20healthcare%20industry%20since%20Taneja%20cofounded%20the%20diabetes%20company%20Livongo%20inside%20GC%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20was%20Livongo's%20largest%20shareholder%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Livongo's%202019%20IPO%2C%20which%20valued%20the%20company%20at%20%242.5%20billion%2C%20making%20GC's%2022%25%20stake%20worth%20more%20than%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteladoc-livongo-insiders-describe-how-the-merger-is-going-2021-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520%252413.9%2520billion%2520deal%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520a%2Cclosed%2520on%2520October%252030%252C%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeladoc%20then%20bought%20Livongo%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20record-breaking%20%2418.5%20billion%20in%202020%2C%20lending%20further%20credence%20to%20Taneja's%20expanding%20healthcare%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hemant%20Taneja%20Glen%20Tullman%20Livongo%20IPO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830a5df6ffb6822ec615dba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222207%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaneja%20with%20the%20Livongo%20team%20at%20its%202019%20IPO.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20NASDAQ%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EModernizing%20healthcare%20has%20long%20been%20a%20passion%20for%20Taneja%2C%20who%20cowrote%20a%20book%20in%202020%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fintendedconsequences.com%2Fbook%2Funhealthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnHealthcare%3A%20A%20Manifesto%20for%20Health%20Assurance%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20advocated%20for%20solutions%20for%20what%20the%20authors%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20healthcare%20debacle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20VC%20firm%20before%20GC%20has%20ever%20acquired%20a%20hospital.%20Those%20deals%20are%20typically%20reserved%20for%20private%20equity%2C%20and%20they've%20recently%20faced%20a%20deluge%20of%20public%20and%20federal%20scrutiny.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-hospitals-bankrupt-closing-wealthy-investors-looting-reselling-private-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteward%20Health%20Care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Massachusetts-based%20system%20of%20nine%20hospitals%20formerly%20owned%20by%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20became%20the%20center%20of%20that%20conversation%20last%20year%20when%20it%20declared%20bankruptcy%2C%20drawing%20ire%20and%20even%20a%20congressional%20inquiry%20over%20reports%20that%20it%20prioritized%20profits%20over%20patient%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20for%20any%20private%20investor%20looking%20to%20play%20hospital%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.generalcatalyst.com%2Fstories%2Fthe-future-of-health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20acquisition%20isn't%20just%20a%20profit%20play.%20The%20firm's%20goal%20isn't%20just%20to%20modernize%20one%20hospital%20system%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wants%20to%20create%20a%20playbook%20for%20health%20systems%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20transform%20Summa%20Health%20by%20improving%20its%20tech%2C%20at%20least%20in%20part%20with%20its%20own%20portfolio%20companies.%20GC%20has%20made%20about%20130%20healthcare%20investments%20to%20date%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website%2C%20including%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-weirdest-startup-commure-blank-check-general-catalyst-hemant-taneja-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%246%20billion%20healthcare%20software%20startup%20Taneja%20cofounded%20and%20a%20likely%20pick%20for%20a%20Summa%20Health%20contract.%20Commure%20has%20become%20an%20umbrella%20for%20other%20healthcare%20companies%2C%20with%20seven%20acquisitions%20under%20its%20belt%20since%20its%202020%20launch%2C%20including%20two%20of%20GC's%20previous%20investments%2C%20Athelas%20and%20Memora%20Health.%20(The%20GC%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20firm%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20reviewing%20technologies%20for%20the%20HATCo%20business%2C%20including%20those%20from%20GC's%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20and%20said%20speculation%20about%20Summa's%20plans%20with%20specific%20companies%20is%20premature.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20is%20also%20banking%20on%20a%20network%20of%20health%20system%20partners%20that%20Taneja%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20growing%2C%20including%20Nashville-based%20HCA%20Healthcare%2C%20which%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20Commure%2C%20and%20Philadelphia-based%20Jefferson%20Health%2C%20which%20notched%20a%20partnership%20in%202021%20to%20work%20with%20several%20of%20GC's%20portfolio%20companies.%20The%20GC%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20healthcare%20ecosystem%20the%20firm%20has%20fostered%20will%20help%20HATCo%20build%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20traditional%20venture%20could%20never%20match.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20a%20really%20powerful%20sourcing%20machine%20that%20they've%20built%2C%20that%20plays%20in%20every%20segment%20of%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20healthcare%20investor%20who%20has%20made%20several%20co-investments%20with%20GC.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20just%20going%20to%20get%20more%20shots%20on%20goal%20than%20other%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20GC's%20returns%20in%20healthcare%20remain%20unrealized.%20And%20its%20healthcare%20portfolio%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20major%20hit%20with%20the%20rapid%20fall%20of%20startup%20Olive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGC%20first%20invested%20in%20Olive%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20automate%20healthcare%20administration%2C%20when%20the%20firm%20led%20a%20%2451%20million%20investment%20into%20the%20company%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Olive%20fell%20into%20the%20classic%20VC%20trap%3A%20raising%20massive%20amounts%20of%20cash%2C%20growing%20too%20fast%2C%20and%20flaming%20out.%20The%20startup%20raised%20%24900%20million%2C%20reaching%20a%20%244%20billion%20valuation%20in%202021.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20Olive%20shut%20down%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20Taneja's%20strategy%20seems%20to%20revolve%20around%20the%20maxim%20that%20bigger%20is%20better.%20It's%20a%20lucrative%20thesis%20for%20VCs%2C%20since%20limited%20partners%20typically%20pay%202%25%20yearly%20fees%20on%20assets%20under%20management%2C%20whether%20the%20investments%20pay%20off%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20firm%20goes%20public%2C%20higher%20fees%20would%20increase%20revenue%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20higher%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaneja%20raised%20eyebrows%20among%20some%20VCs%20when%20he%20recently%20addressed%20fees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fhemanttaneja_theres-been-a-recent-narrative-in-some-venture-activity-7318649443581317120-ShyM%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20LinkedIn%20post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20recent%20narrative%20in%20some%20venture%20circles%20about%20'AUM%20maxxing'%E2%80%94that%20firms%20(like%20ours)%20are%20focused%20on%20growing%20assets%20under%20management%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20fees%20rather%20than%20long-term%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20arguing%20that%20funds%20will%20still%20be%20judged%20on%20their%20distributions.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20true%20that%20scaling%20platforms%20can%20bring%20new%20complexity%E2%80%94and%20that%20fund%20multiples%20may%20compress%20over%20time.%20But%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20value%20at%20scale%20is%20greater%20than%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20founders%20could%20feel%20lost%20among%20more%20than%20800%20companies%2C%20Porter%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Collaborative%20Robotics%2C%20says%20GC's%20scale%20has%20been%20a%20major%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Hemant%20is%20really%20doing%20is%20trying%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20the%20biggest%20thinkers%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Porter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20after%20the%20deal%20closes%2C%20he%20hopes%20GC%20will%20help%20him%20sell%20his%20robots%20to%20Summa%20Health.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20founder%2C%20that's%20an%20amazing%20set%20of%20resources%20to%20tap%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-catalyst-hemant-taneja-redefine-venture-capital-baffling-industry-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748422802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682221cac6ad288d1480a941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-catalyst-hemant-taneja-redefine-venture-capital-baffling-industry-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22General%20Catalyst%20is%20quietly%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20to%20become%20the%20first%20VC%20firm%20to%20go%20public.%20Its%20strategy%20is%20baffling%20the%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman%2CRebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%