%20decline%20since%20the%20financial%20crisis%20of%202008.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fpolicy%2F406604%2Fabundance-ezra-klein-housing-yimby-pronatalism-birth-rates-donald-trump-ivf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20factors%3C%2Fa%3E%20influence%20the%20choice%20to%20have%20kids%2C%20government%20policy%20is%20well-positioned%20to%20address%20the%20economic%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20evidence%20that%20rising%20housing%20costs%20shrink%20family%20size.%20A%2010%25%20increase%20in%20home%20prices%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fdigest%2Ffeb12%2Fimpact-real-estate-market-fertility%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%25%20decrease%20in%20births%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20non-homeowners%2C%20economists%20Lisa%20Dettling%20and%20Melissa%20Schettini%20Kearney%20found%20in%20a%202012%20paper%20published%20in%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20found%20evidence%20from%20the%20distant%20past%20that%20easier%20access%20to%20homeownership%20can%20help%20boost%20birth%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advent%20of%20the%20modern%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fva-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-down-payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20mortgage%20in%20the%201930s%20facilitated%20a%20sharp%20uptick%20in%20the%20US%20birth%20rate%20that%20helped%20create%20the%20baby%20boom%2C%20according%20to%20their%20February%202025%20NBER%20working%20paper.%20The%20loans%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20Federal%20Housing%20Administration%20and%20the%20Veterans%20Administration%2C%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20some%20younger%20Americans%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20by%20allowing%20very%20low%20payments%20up%20front%20and%2030%20years%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20loans.%20(Black%20Americans%20were%20effectively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-redlining-kept-black-americans-from-homeownership-and-still-does-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcluded%20from%20these%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20two%20mortgage%20insurance%20programs%20helped%20lower%20the%20age%20people%20got%20married%20and%20had%20their%20first%20baby%2C%20and%20led%20to%203%20million%20additional%20births%20between%201935%20and%201957%2C%20accounting%20for%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20spike%20in%20births%20associated%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistorical-events-defined-boomer-generation-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20have%20kids%20is%20less%20about%20can%20they%20take%20three%20months%20off%20work%20versus%20'do%20I%20have%20a%20bedroom%20to%20put%20this%20kid%20in%20for%20the%20next%2018%20years%3F'%26quot%3B%20Schettini%20Kearney%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetting-mortage-downpayment-housing-helped-raise-birth-rates-baby-boomers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-babies-birth-rates-natalism-cheaper-housing-costs-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748419502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f446cc6ad288d1481a760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-babies-birth-rates-natalism-cheaper-housing-costs-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20report%20found%20that%20housing%20costs%20were%20the%20single%20biggest%20factor%20stopping%20Americans%20from%20having%20the%20number%20of%20kids%20they%20want.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22erelman%40businessinsider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22e