20one%20stitch%20at%20a%20time.%20His%20legacy%20now%20lives%20on%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20next%20generation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParray%20is%20speaking%20to%20a%20more%20profound%20shift%20that%20many%20in%20the%20valley%20have%20witnessed%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades.%20As%20mass-produced%20shawls%20flooded%20the%20market%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20authentic%20Jamawar%2C%20which%20requires%20weeks%2C%20even%20months%20of%20meticulous%20handwork%2C%20struggled%20to%20compete%20on%20price%20and%20visibility.%20Yet%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20artisans%2C%20including%20Haji%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Khan%2C%20continued%20to%20work%20the%20old%20way%2C%20thread%20by%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20is%20known%20for%20his%20patchwork%20pieces%20and%20his%20mastery%20of%20traditional%20Sozni%20and%20Kani%20embroidery%20techniques%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20which%20demand%20intense%20labour%2C%20precision%2C%20and%20years%20of%20experience%20to%20perfect.%20His%20reputation%20has%20grown%20well%20beyond%20Kashmir.%20As%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Art%20%26amp%3B%20Craft%20Development%20Society%2C%20he%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20voices%20for%20artisan%20welfare%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Khan%20has%20participated%20in%20international%20exhibitions%20and%20emporia%2C%20taking%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20craft%20traditions%20to%20global%20platforms.%20His%20displays%20are%20often%20among%20the%20most%20admired%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20for%20their%20visual%20intricacy%2C%20but%20for%20the%20history%20they%20carry%20in%20every%20motif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeritage%20in%20demand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Khan%2C%20Jamawar%20Pashmina%20shawls%20are%20primarily%20sold%20in%20India%2C%20but%20they%20also%20find%20buyers%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20Brazil%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20and%20across%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%E2%