20inherited.%20Each%20thread%20tells%20a%20story%20of%20Kashmiri%20heritage%20and%20timeless%20craft.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-439246%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJamawar%20shawls%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20worn%20%E2%80%94%20they%E2%80%99re%20inherited.%20Each%20thread%20tells%20a%20story%20of%20Kashmiri%20heritage%20and%20timeless%20craft.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Shahkaar%20(L)%20and%20The%20House%20of%20Naqash%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20ensure%20its%20longevity%2C%20he%20is%20breathing%20new%20life%20into%20a%20forgotten%20art%20form%20and%20is%20actively%20working%20to%20pass%20it%20down%20to%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20envisioning%20a%20legacy%20that%20will%20thrive%20for%20centuries%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20take%20this%20art%20forward%2C%20but%20the%20government%20should%20establish%20a%20dedicated%20training%20centre%20where%20aspiring%20artisans%20and%20young%20students%20can%20learn%20the%20craft%20with%20ease.%20The%20work%20is%20demanding%2C%20and%20a%20single%20shawl%20can%20take%20months%20or%20even%20years%20to%20complete.%20It%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20shawl%20from%20scratch%20until%20completion.%20The%20work%20demands%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%2C%20which%20is%20why%20people%20are%20fleeing%20from%20this%20art%20and%20refusing%20to%20learn%20it.%20It%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20patience%20and%20skill%20that%20define%20this%20timeless%20Kashmiri%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreserving%20art%20amid%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20with%20his%20grey%20flowing%20beard%2C%20adds%20that%20handicraft%20demands%20patience%2C%20a%20quality%20often%20lacking%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20worked%20on%20a%20project%2C%20a%2064-piece%20shawl%2C%20which%20took%20over%20five%20years%20to%20complete%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20apprentices.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20have%20patience%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20reintroduced%20the%20forgotten%20art%20of%20Jamawar%20shawl-making.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20septuagenarian%20claims%20that%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20there%20is%20not%20a%20single%20artisan%20in%20the%20Valley%20who%20can%20create%20Jamawar%20patchwork%20on%20shawls%20as%20he%20does.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20can%20do%20Jamawar%20work%20like%20I%20do.%20Though%20I%20have%20trained%20many%20people%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20my%20brother%2C%20they%20lack%20the%20accuracy%20and%20dedication%20required%20for%20this%20craft.%20I%20would%20be%20over%20the%20moon%20to%20see%20artisans%20stepping%20into%20my%20shoes%2C%20and%20they%20would%20also%20get%20all%20the%20awards%20I%20receive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Khan%2C%20another%20reason%20Jamawar%20work%20has%20struggled%20to%20progress%20is%20the%20declining%20respect%20for%20handicrafts%20in%20Kashmir.%20A%20growing%20craze%20for%20white-collar%20jobs%20has%20led%20many%20to%20look%20down%20on%20traditional%20artisan%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Director%20of%20Handicrafts%20and%20Handloom%20Kashmir%2C%20Mussarat%20Islam%2C%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20432%20centres%20across%20Kashmir%20are%20currently%20functioning%20under%20the%20department%2C%20where%20various%20traditional%20art%20forms%2C%20including%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Jamawar%20patchwork%2C%20are%20officially%20recognised%20and%20taught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20each%20centre%2C%20skilled%20artisans%2C%20including%204%20to%205%20master%20craftsmen%20like%20Khan%20are%20training%20budding%20artists%20who%20also%20receive%20stipends%20and%20allowances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20further%20promote%20Jamawar%20patchwork%2C%20we%20are%20actively%20introducing%20it%20under%20various%20government%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20preserving%20and%20expanding%20this%20heritage%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20workshop%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20unusual%20to%20find%20young%20men%20and%20women%20sitting%20beside%20him%2C%20observing%2C%20asking%20questions%2C%20learning%20slowly%20%E2%80%94%20stitch%20by%20stitch.%20Some%20come%20from%20families%20of%20artisans%2C%20others%20are%20drawn%20by%20curiosity.%20What%20they%20all%20share%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20keep%20something%20alive%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20a%20technique%2C%20but%20a%20way%20of%20seeing%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20traditional%20crafts%20are%20often%20reduced%20to%20souvenirs%2C%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20story%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20quiet%20work%20being%20done%20across%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%94%20reminds%20us%20that%20these%20art%20forms%20still%20have%20life%2C%20meaning%2C%20and%20a%20future%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20people%20who%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748265369000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D439194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20life-changing%20accident%20in%201998%2C%20Srinagar-based%20artisan%20Haji%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Khan%20returned%20to%20the%20forg